node.text: Who remembers this episode??? Honey this was one of the funniest Fridays with Tab and Chance moments😂. We were playing a Q&A game with @choycebrown and honey I got caught up in my answer and she was done with me and @teamchancebasketball 😂😂😂 Whi can relate??? We can’t wait to get back to y’all real soon!! Until then, enjoy this memory and good laugh with us!  Love y’all! #fridayswithtabandchance #tabithabrown #chancebrown

node.text:
4 years ago I was driving Uber and would often drop people off at the Van Nuys Airport for their private flights.  Today, God said it was my turn!! 
🙌🏿OOHH GOD I THANK YOU🙌🏿 
I feel so blessed to be on this journey and to share this moment with my baby girl, makes it even more special! Dreams that I never even imagined are coming true!! Can’t wait to share what we are working on together 🙌🏿❤️ Something special coming soon!! #ThankyouGod #tabithabrown #choycebrown #motherdaughter

node.text: Who remembers this episode??? Honey this was one of the funniest Fridays with Tab and Chance moments😂. We were playing a Q&A game with @choycebrown and honey I got caught up in my answer and she was done with me and @teamchancebasketball 😂😂😂 Whi can relate??? We can’t wait to get back to y’all real soon!! Until then, enjoy this memory and good laugh with us!  Love y’all! #fridayswithtabandchance #tabithabrown #chancebrown
